# 🚀 How to Run DocuGuard

Three ways to run — pick based on your situation.

---

## Method 1 — CLI Demo (No Telegram Needed) ⚡

Fastest way to see the cryptography in action. No bot token required.

```bash
# 1. Clone or download the project
cd docuguard

# 2. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 3. Run the demo
python src/demo_cli.py
```

**What you'll see:**
```
