## 🔧 Troubleshooting

| Error | Fix |
|---|---|
| `ModuleNotFoundError: telegram` | Run `pip install python-telegram-bot==21.5` |
| `ModuleNotFoundError: dotenv` | Run `pip install python-dotenv` |
| `Conflict: terminated by other getUpdates` | Only one instance of the bot can run at a time — stop the other one |
| `Unauthorized` | Your bot token is wrong — double-check `.env` |
| Bot doesn't respond | Make sure the terminal is still running (bot must stay open) |

